McIlroy Wins U.S. Open for First Major Golf Title

-- B y   D e x   M c L u s k e y
-- 
2011-06-19T23:27:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-19/mcilroy-wins-u-s-open-for-first-major-golf-title.html
Rory McIlroy won the U.S. Open by
eight shots for his first major golf title.  The 22-year-old from  Northern Ireland  had a final round 2-
under-par 69 for a four-round total of 16-under 268 at
Congressional Country Club in Bethesda,  Maryland .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dex McLuskey at 
 dmcluskey@bloomberg.net  